type.title: Short title.
type.context: PROTOCOL TO THE AGREEMENT ESTABLISHING THE  CARIBBEAN COURT OF JUSTICE ACT under Short title. 1.   This Act may be cited as the Protocol to the Agreement Establishing the Caribbean Court of Justice Act.

act: PROTOCOL TO THE AGREEMENT ESTABLISHING THE  CARIBBEAN COURT OF JUSTICE ACT

type.name: section
type.title: Interpretation.
type.context: PROTOCOL TO THE AGREEMENT ESTABLISHING THE  CARIBBEAN COURT OF JUSTICE ACT under Interpretation. 2.   In this Act Protocol means the Protocol to the Agreement Establishing the Caribbean Court of Justice, signed at Montego Bay, Jamaica on 4th July, 2003, the text of which is set out in the Schedule.
